3	Mirrors ``nba_playoff.simulation.distributions`` but adapts team-data aggregation
4	to the football train_data.csv schema: columns are ``HOME_TEAM``, ``AWAY_TEAM``,
5	10 feature columns (5 home + 5 away), and ``HOME_WIN``.  Per-team historical
6	observations are gathered by combining the *_home columns from rows where the
7	team played at home with the *_away columns from rows where the team played away.
